scaledmarkets.dabl.helper

Class Helper

  • java.lang.Object
    • scaledmarkets.dabl.helper.Helper

  • public class Helper
extends java.lang.Object
    Convenience methods for traversing the final AST and Annotations that are produced by the DABL compiler.
